## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="ba176-285">クラスの<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Password%2A> <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Username%2A> プロパティとプロパティを次の例に示します<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ba176-285">The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Username%2A> and <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Password%2A> properties of the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ba176-286">この例では、ユーザーが<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry>指定し<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Path%2A>たと、 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Children%2A>そのすべてのを取得します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ba176-286">This example gets the user-specified <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> and the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Path%2A> of all its <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Children%2A>.</span></span>  
  
